# Fiscal printer IP address setup
To enable proper communication between LS Express and the Epson fiscal printer, it is necessary to enter the IP address configured in the fiscal printer setup.
The association between the IP address and the POS number (POS Id) is managed through the “Fiscal Printer Setup” function available on the LS Express subscription management page.

<img width="" src="https://docs-test.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR001139-0/IPStampante1ENU.jpg"><br>

For each POS (point of sale) listed, it is possible to assign an IP address in the “Fiscal Printer IP Address” field.

